                "name": "Barbed Hairs",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A tarantula can throw barbed hairs from its back at a creature as a ranged touch attack (range increment 20 feet). A creature struck by these hairs must make a DC 22 Fort save or be nauseated for 1d6 rounds. A creature that attacks a giant tarantula with a non-reach melee weapon must make a DC 22 Reflex save to avoid being struck by these hairs. The save DC is Con-based."
            },
